   "source": [
    "# Disaster Priority Map: Connecting Satellite Imagery with Crisis Tweets\n",
    "**Zero-Shot Cross-Modal Alignment using CLIP Embeddings**\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook:\n",
    "1. Loads EuroSAT satellite tiles + disaster tweets (no paired training data)\n",
    "2. Encodes both into a shared CLIP vector space\n",
    "3. Scores each image tile against crisis tweets using cosine similarity\n",
    "4. Outputs a geographic priority heatmap\n"
   ]
  },
